## 3 · Frontend Architecture

### 3.1 Tech Stack

| Technology | Version | Role |
|---|---|---|
| **Angular** | 21.2 | Component framework (Standalone components, Signals) |
| **TailwindCSS** | 4.x | Utility-first styling via PostCSS |
| **RxJS** | 7.8 | Async HTTP communication |
| **TypeScript** | 5.9 | Type safety |
| **SSR** | `@angular/ssr` | Server-side rendering support (Express) |

### 3.2 File Structure

```
src/app/
├── app.ts                    # Root component (imports MovieSearchComponent)
├── app.html                  # Root template (<router-outlet> + component)
├── app.config.ts             # provideHttpClient, provideRouter, hydration
├── app.routes.ts             # Empty routes (single-page app)
├── components/
│   └── movie-search/
│       ├── movie-search.component.ts     # Component logic (Signals)
│       └── movie-search.component.html   # Full UI template
└── services/
    └── movie.service.ts      # HTTP client, error handling
```

### 3.3 Component Architecture

```mermaid
graph TD
    Root["App (root component)"] --> Search["MovieSearchComponent"]
    Search --> SVC["MovieService"]
    SVC -->|"HttpClient GET"| API["Backend API :8000"]

    style Root fill:#6366f1,color:#fff
    style Search fill:#8b5cf6,color:#fff
    style SVC fill:#a855f7,color:#fff
    style API fill:#059669,color:#fff
```

#### MovieSearchComponent ([movie-search.component.ts](file:///d:/Code/Python/MovieRecommendationSystem/Frontend/MovieRecommendationSystem/src/app/components/movie-search/movie-search.component.ts))

Uses **Angular Signals** for reactive state:

| Signal | Type | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `loading` | `boolean` | Shows spinner, disables input/button |
| `errorMessage` | `string \| null` | Displays error alert |
| [recommendations](file:///d:/Code/Python/MovieRecommendationSystem/Backend/main.py#21-34) | `string[]` | The 5 recommended movie titles |
| `currentMovie` | `string \| null` | The movie that was searched |
| `isDarkMode` | `boolean` | Toggles light/dark theme |

**Search flow**: User types → [searchMovie()](file:///d:/Code/Python/MovieRecommendationSystem/Frontend/MovieRecommendationSystem/src/app/components/movie-search/movie-search.component.ts#26-47) → sets `loading(true)` → calls `MovieService.getRecommendations()` → on success, sets [recommendations](file:///d:/Code/Python/MovieRecommendationSystem/Backend/main.py#21-34) + `currentMovie`; on error, sets `errorMessage`.

#### MovieService ([movie.service.ts](file:///d:/Code/Python/MovieRecommendationSystem/Frontend/MovieRecommendationSystem/src/app/services/movie.service.ts))

- **Base URL**: `http://localhost:8000`
- Sends `GET /recommend?movie_name=<encoded_title>`
- Returns `Observable<MovieRecommendationResponse>`
- Error handling: distinguishes client-side vs. server-side errors, surfaces 404 as "Movie not found"

### 3.4 UI Features

| Feature | Implementation |
|---|---|
| **Dark/Light mode** | Signal toggle + TailwindCSS `dark:` variants |
| **Enter-to-search** | [(keyup.enter)="searchMovie()"](file:///d:/Code/Python/MovieRecommendationSystem/Frontend/MovieRecommendationSystem/src/app/app.ts#5-14) on input |
| **Loading state** | Button shows spinner + "Searching…", input disabled |
| **Error display** | Red alert banner with icon |
| **Results grid** | Responsive 1→2→3 column card grid |
| **Hover effects** | Cards lift + shadow on hover with gradient overlay |

### 3.5 How It Runs

```bash
# From /Frontend/MovieRecommendationSystem directory
ng serve    # starts on http://localhost:4200 (proxies to :8000)
```

---

## 4 · Communication Between Frontend & Backend

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    A["Angular :4200"] -- "CORS-enabled HTTP" --> B["FastAPI :8000"]
```

- **CORS**: Backend allows all origins (`allow_origins=["*"]`) so the Angular dev server at `:4200` can call the API at `:8000`.
- **Data format**: JSON over HTTP GET, no authentication.
- **Response structure**:

```json
{
  "movie": "Inception",
  "recommendations": [
    "Interstellar",
    "The Dark Knight",
    "The Prestige",
    "Shutter Island",
    "Memento"
  ]
}
```

